This mod add 1 Alley at outside of Riften.
Daggercross Alley is small blind side of Crossed Daggers.
descriptionHtml:
This mod add 1 Alley at outside of Riften.
Daggercross Alley is small blind side of Crossed Daggers.

Shady merchant, illicit fence, courier, rogue...
Daggercross Alley is swamp of people like that.
No guards, No law, No guild\'s rule.
This is Daggercross Alley.

If you are some kind of outlaw or illicit thief, lockpicks, poisons and potions, illicit fence are useful for you.
If you want sweet skooma or sweet moon sugar, You\'ve come to the right place.
If you are guild thief or crusader, close out or let it lie...as you choose.

I\'m glad if you like it.

This mod was cleaned by TES5Edit made by ElminsterEU.
Many many thanks for him and team.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/25859

If you like this mod, please check my other mods.
